def register_create(request):
    """
    This view will log the new user or throw an error if something is wrong.
    Redirect to register_view to disallow resubmit of the form.
    """
    if not request.POST:
        raise Http404()
    POST = request.POST
    request.session["register_form_data"] = POST
    form = RegisterForm(POST)

    """
    This class verifies if the user is owner of the account to have
    acess to specific actions like create, update or delete a recipe.
    """
    def has_object_permission(self, request, view, obj):
        return obj.author == request.user
